    SUM(B_store_views) * 1.0 / SUM(B_clicks) as B_conversion_rate
  FROM `ab_testing.ab_FreshFood`
  UNION ALL
  SELECT 
    'Gaming' as scenario,
    SUM(A_store_views) * 1.0 / SUM(A_clicks) as A_conversion_rate,
    SUM(B_store_views) * 1.0 / SUM(B_clicks) as B_conversion_rate
  FROM `ab_testing.ab_Gaming`
  UNION ALL
  SELECT 
    'Health' as scenario,
    SUM(A_store_views) * 1.0 / SUM(A_clicks) as A_conversion_rate,
    SUM(B_store_views) * 1.0 / SUM(B_clicks) as B_conversion_rate
  FROM `ab_testing.ab_Health`
  UNION ALL
  SELECT 
    'Home' as scenario,
    SUM(A_store_views) * 1.0 / SUM(A_clicks) as A_conversion_rate,

  SELECT

  FROM `ab_testing.ab_Hospitality`
  UNION ALL
  SELECT 
    'Music' as scenario,
    SUM(A_store_views) * 1.0 / SUM(A_clicks) as A_conversion_rate,
    SUM(B_store_views) * 1.0 / SUM(B_clicks) as B_conversion_rate
  FROM `ab_testing.ab_Music`
  UNION ALL
  SELECT 
    'Office' as scenario,
    SUM(A_store_views) * 1.0 / SUM(A_clicks) as A_conversion_rate,
    SUM(B_store_views) * 1.0 / SUM(B_clicks) as B_conversion_rate
  FROM `ab_testing.ab_Office`
  UNION ALL
  SELECT 
    'Outdoor' as scenario,
    SUM(A_store_views) * 1.0 / SUM(A_clicks) as A_conversion_rate,
    SUM(B_store_views) * 1.0 / SUM(B_clicks) as B_conversion_rate
  FROM `ab_testing.ab_Outdoor`
  UNION ALL
  SELECT 
    'Pets' as scenario,
    SUM(A_store_views) * 1.0 / SUM(A_clicks) as A_conversion_rate,
    SUM(B_store_views) * 1.0 / SUM(B_clicks) as B_conversion_rate
  FROM `ab_testing.ab_Pets`

    'Sports' as scenario,

  FROM `ab_testing.ab_Travel`
)
SELECT 
  scenario,
  ROUND(A_conversion_rate, 4) as A_conversion_rate,
  ROUND(B_conversion_rate, 4) as B_conversion_rate,
  ROUND(B_conversion_rate - A_conversion_rate, 4) as difference
FROM conversion_rates

        SUM(A_clicks) as A_clicks,

        SUM(B_store_views) as B_store_views
    FROM `ab_testing.ab_Hospitality`
    
UNION ALL

        SUM(A_clicks) as A_clicks,

        SUM(B_clicks) as B_clicks,
        SUM(B_store_views) as B_store_views
    FROM `ab_testing.ab_Music`
    
UNION ALL

        SUM(B_clicks) as B_clicks,
        SUM(B_store_views) as B_store_views
    FROM `ab_testing.ab_Pets`
    
UNION ALL

    SELECT 'Sports' as scenario,
        SUM(A_clicks) as A_clicks,
        SUM(A_store_views) as A_store_views,
        SUM(B_clicks) as B_clicks,
        SUM(B_store_views) as B_store_views

        SUM(A_clicks) as A_clicks,

        SUM(B_clicks) as B_clicks,
        SUM(B_store_views) as B_store_views

    A_clicks,
    A_store_views,

    B_store_views,

        SUM(A_clicks) as A_clicks,
        SUM(A_store_views) as A_store_views,
        SUM(B_clicks) as B_clicks,
        SUM(B_store_views) as B_store_views
    FROM `ab_testing.ab_Pets`
    UNION ALL
    SELECT 'Sports' as scenario,
        SUM(A_clicks) as A_clicks,
        SUM(A_store_views) as A_store_views,
        SUM(B_clicks) as B_clicks,
        SUM(B_store_views) as B_store_views
    FROM `ab_testing.ab_Sports`
    UNION ALL
    SELECT 'Travel' as scenario,
        SUM(A_clicks) as A_clicks,
        SUM(A_store_views) as A_store_views,
        SUM(B_clicks) as B_clicks,
        SUM(B_store_views) as B_store_views
    FROM `ab_testing.ab_Travel`
)
SELECT 
    scenario,
    A_clicks,
    A_store_views,
    B_clicks,
    B_store_views,
    A_clicks + B_clicks as total_clicks,
    A_store_views + B_store_views as total_store_views,
    CAST(A_store_views AS FLOAT64)/NULLIF(A_clicks,0) as A_conv,
    CAST(B_store_views AS FLOAT64)/NULLIF(B_clicks,0) as B_conv,
    CAST(A_store_views + B_store_views AS FLOAT64)/NULLIF(A_clicks + B_clicks,0) as combined_conv
FROM per_scenario
ORDER BY scenario
